import { View, ImageBackground, Image, StyleSheet } from 'react-native'
import React from 'react'
import Text from '../../components/Text'
import images from '../../assets/image/'
import { HEIGHT, WIDTH } from '../../assets/styles'

export default function Profile() {
    return (
        <View>
            <ImageBackground
                source={images.BG_PROFILE}
                resizeMode='cover'
                style={styles.background}
            >
                <View style={{ borderWidth: 2, borderColor: '#FBD2A5', borderRadius: 90 }}>
                    <Image
                        source={images.PERSON2}
                        style={styles.person}
                    ></Image>
                </View>
                <Text fontSize={20} bold style={{ marginTop: 16 }}>Ahmad Akbar Maulana</Text>
                <Text bold color="#909090" style={{ paddingBottom: 32 }}>React Native Developer</Text>
                <View style={{

                }}>
                    <View style={{ justifyContent: "space-between", padding: 5, flexDirection: "row" }}>
                        <Text fontSize={14} bold style={{ paddingTop: 16 }}>ID</Text>
                        <Text fontSize={14} color="#A7A7A7" style={{ paddingTop: 16, paddingLeft: 16 }}>A20134</Text>
                    </View>
                    <View style={{ paddingTop: 13, paddingleft: 16, paddjustifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center' }}>
                        <View style={{ paddingLeft: 16, height: 1, width: 311.00644, borderBottomColor: '#D3D3D3', borderBottomWidth: 1 }} />
                    </View>

                    <View style={{ justifyContent: "space-between", padding: 5, flexDirection: "row" }}>
                        <Text fontSize={14} bold style={{ paddingTop: 16 }}>Email</Text>
                        <Text fontSize={14} color="#A7A7A7" style={{ paddingTop: 16, paddingLeft: 16 }}>siapayaamanyanyah@gmail.com</Text>
                    </View>

                    <View style={{ paddingTop: 13, paddingleft: 16, paddjustifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center' }}>
                        <View style={{ paddingLeft: 16, height: 1, width: 311.00644, borderBottomColor: '#D3D3D3', borderBottomWidth: 1 }} />
                    </View>

                    <View style={{ justifyContent: "space-between", padding: 5, flexDirection: "row" }}>
                        <Text fontSize={14} bold style={{ paddingTop: 16 }}>Date of Birth</Text>
                        <Text fontSize={14} color="#A7A7A7" style={{ paddingTop: 16, paddingLeft: 16 }}>3 May 1999</Text>
                    </View>

                    <View style={{ paddingTop: 13, paddingleft: 16, paddjustifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center' }}>
                        <View style={{ paddingHorizontal: 16, height: 1, width: 311.00644, borderBottomColor: '#D3D3D3', borderBottomWidth: 1 }} />
                    </View>
                    <View style={{ justifyContent: "space-between", padding: 5, flexDirection: "row" }}>
                        <Text fontSize={14} bold style={{ paddingTop: 16, paddingBottom: 16 }}>Gender</Text>
                        <Text fontSize={14} color="#A7A7A7" style={{ paddingTop: 16, paddingLeft: 16, paddingBottom: 16 }}>Male</Text>
                    </View>
                </View>
                <View style={{
                    marginTop: 20,
                    width: 343,
                    height: 70,
                    paddingTopP: 20,
                    paddingHorizontal: 16,
                    backgroundColor: "#fff",
                    borderRadius: 12,
                    shadowColor: '#000',
                    shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
                    shadowOpacity: 0.3,
                    shadowRadius: 4,
                    elevation: 5,
                    marginHorizontal: 16
                }}>
                    <View style={{ marginRight: -16, justifyContent: "space-between", padding: 5, flexDirection: "row" }}>
                        <View>
                            <Text fontSize={14} bold style={{ paddingTop: 16 }}>Team</Text>
                            <Text fontSize={14} color="#A7A7A7" >React Native</Text>
                        </View>
                        <View>
                        </View>
                        <Image
                            source={images.PERSON3}
                            style={{
                                width: 35,
                                height: 35,
                                borderRadius: 90,
                                marginLeft: 'auto',
                                border: 1,
                                borderColor: "#FFF",
                                marginRight: 16,
                                marginTop: 17,
                                marginBottom: 17,
                            }}

                        ></Image>
                        <Image
                            source={images.PERSON4}
                            style={{
                                width: 35,
                                height: 35,
                                borderRadius: 90,
                                border: 1,
                                borderColor: "#FFF",
                                marginLeft: -30,
                                marginRight: 16,
                                marginTop: 17,
                                marginBottom: 17,
                            }}
                        ></Image>
                        <Image
                            source={images.PERSON5}
                            style={{
                                width: 35,
                                height: 35,
                                borderRadius: 90,
                                border: 1,
                                borderColor: "#FFF",
                                marginLeft: -30,
                                marginRight: 16,
                                marginTop: 17,
                                marginBottom: 17,

                            }}
                        ></Image>
                        <Image
                            source={images.ELIPSE}
                            style={{
                                width: 35,
                                height: 35,
                                borderRadius: 90,
                                border: 1,
                                borderColor: "#FFF",
                                marginLeft: -30,
                                marginRight: 16,
                                marginTop: 17,
                                marginBottom: 17,

                            }}
                        ></Image>
                        <Text color="#FFFF" style={{
                            marginLeft: -43,
                            marginRight: 25,
                            marginTop: 25,
                            marginBottom: 26,

                        }}>+6</Text>
                    </View>
                    <View style={{
                        alignSelf: "center",
                        marginTop: 10,
                        width: 343,
                        height: 186,
                        paddingHorizontal: 16,
                        backgroundColor: "#fff",
                        borderRadius: 12,
                        shadowColor: '#000',
                        shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
                        shadowOpacity: 0.3,
                        shadowRadius: 4,
                        elevation: 5,
                    }}>
                        <View style={{ flexDirection: "row", justifyContent: "space-between", alignItems: "center" }}>
                            <View style={{ flexDirection: "row", alignItems: "center" }}>
                                <Image
                                    source={images.GUARD}
                                    style={{
                                        width: 24,
                                        height: 24,
                                        borderRadius: 90,
                                        borderWidth: 1,
                                        borderColor: "#FFF",
                                        marginTop: 14,
                                        marginRight: 11
                                    }}
                                ></Image>
                                <Text fontSize={14} bold style={{ marginTop: 16, alignSelf: 'center' }}>Privacy And Security</Text>
                            </View>
                            <Image
                                source={images.VECTOR}
                                color="#292D32"
                                style={{
                                    marginTop: 20,
                                    width: 5,
                                    height: 11,

                                }}
                            ></Image>
                        </View>
                        <View style={{ paddingTop: 9, paddjustifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center' }}>
                            <View style={{ width: 311.00644, borderBottomColor: '#D3D3D3', borderBottomWidth: 1 }} />
                        </View>
                        <View style={{ flexDirection: "row", justifyContent: "space-between", alignItems: "center" }}>
                            <View style={{ flexDirection: "row", alignItems: "center" }}>
                                <Image
                                    source={images.HELP}
                                    style={{
                                        width: 24,
                                        height: 24,
                                        borderRadius: 90,
                                        borderWidth: 1,
                                        borderColor: "#FFF",
                                        marginTop: 12,
                                        marginRight: 11
                                    }}
                                ></Image>
                                <Text fontSize={14} bold style={{ marginTop: 16, alignSelf: 'center' }}>Help</Text>
                            </View>
                            <Image
                                source={images.VECTOR}
                                color="#292D32"
                                style={{
                                    marginTop: 20,
                                    width: 5,
                                    height: 11,
                                }}
                            ></Image>
                        </View>
                        <View style={{ paddingTop: 9, paddjustifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center' }}>
                            <View style={{ width: 311.00644, borderBottomColor: '#D3D3D3', borderBottomWidth: 1 }} />
                        </View>
                        <View style={{ flexDirection: "row", justifyContent: "space-between", alignItems: "center" }}>
                            <View style={{ flexDirection: "row", alignItems: "center" }}>
                                <Image
                                    source={images.ABOUT}
                                    style={{
                                        width: 24,
                                        height: 24,
                                        borderRadius: 90,
                                        borderWidth: 1,
                                        borderColor: "#FFF",
                                        marginTop: 12,
                                        marginRight: 11
                                    }}
                                ></Image>
                                <Text fontSize={14} bold style={{ marginTop: 16, alignSelf: 'center' }}>About Us</Text>
                            </View>
                            <Image
                                source={images.VECTOR}
                                color="#292D32"
                                style={{
                                    marginTop: 20,
                                    width: 5,
                                    height: 11,

                                }}
                            ></Image>
                        </View>
                        <View style={{ paddingTop: 9, paddjustifyContent: 'center', alignItems: 'center' }}>
                            <View style={{ width: 311.00644, borderBottomColor: '#D3D3D3', borderBottomWidth: 1 }} />
                        </View>
                        <View style={{ flexDirection: "row", justifyContent: "space-between", alignItems: "center" }}>
                            <View style={{ flexDirection: "row", alignItems: "center" }}>
                                <Image
                                    source={images.LOGOUT}
                                    style={{
                                        width: 24,
                                        height: 24,
                                        borderRadius: 90,
                                        borderWidth: 1,
                                        borderColor: "#FFF",
                                        marginTop: 12,
                                        marginRight: 11
                                    }}
                                ></Image>
                                <Text fontSize={14} bold style={{ marginTop: 16, alignSelf: 'center' }}>Logout</Text>
                            </View>
                            <Image
                                source={images.VECTOR}
                                color="#292D32"
                                style={{
                                    marginTop: 20,
                                    width: 5,
                                    height: 11,

                                }}
                            ></Image>
                        </View>
                        <View>
                            <Text fontSize={14} bold style={{ paddingTop: 20, alignSelf: "center" }}>v.0.0.1</Text>
                        </View>

                        <View style={{ flexDirection: "row", justifyContent: "space-between", alignItems: "center" }}>

                            <Image
                                source={images.HOME}
                                color="#292D32"
                                style={{

                                    marginLeft: -5,
                                    width: 24,
                                    height: 25,
                                }}
                            ></Image>
                            <Image
                                source={images.TASK}
                                color="#292D32"
                                style={{

                                    marginLeft: 25,
                                    width: 28,
                                    height: 25,
                                }}
                            ></Image>
                            <Image
                                source={images.BG}
                                color="#292D32"
                                style={{
                                    width: 120,
                                    height: 120,
                                }}
                            ></Image>
                            <Image
                                source={images.PERFORM}
                                color="#292D32"
                                style={{
                                    marginRight: 25,
                                    width: 25,
                                    height: 26,
                                }}
                            ></Image>
                            <Image
                                source={images.PROFILE}
                                color="#292D32"
                                style={{
                                    marginRight: -10,
                                    width: 21,
                                    height: 24,
                                }}
                            ></Image>
                        </View>
                        <View style={{ marginTop: -45, flexDirection: "row", justifyContent: "space-between", alignItems: "center" }}>
                            <Text fontSize={10} style={{ marginLeft: -5 }}>Home</Text>
                            <Text fontSize={10} style={{ marginLeft: 40 }}>Task</Text>
                            <Text fontSize={10} style={{ marginLeft: 135 }}>Performance</Text>
                            <Text color='#04325F' bold fontSize={10} style={{ marginLeft: 21, paddingRight: 29 }}>Profile</Text>
                        </View>
                    </View>
                </View>
                {/* <Text fontSize={36} bold color={"green"} >Ini Test Fonts
                </Text> */}
            </ImageBackground>
        </View>
    )
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
    background: {
        width: WIDTH,
        height: 495,
        paddingTop: 90,
        alignItems: 'center',
    },
    person:{
        width: 120,
        height: 120,
        borderRadius: 90,
    },
    rectang:{
        paddingHorizontal: 16,
        backgroundColor: "#fff",
        borderRadius: 12,
        shadowColor: '#000',
        shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
        shadowOpacity: 0.3,
        shadowRadius: 4,
        elevation: 5,
        marginHorizontal: 20,
    }
});
